##My mother-in-law is a God

Micro Signal RSZMDFJ

Function introduction, human is the scale of all things, human is the most beautiful scenery.

Mother in Law 20190516 in Wuhan

February 23,2020.

The first day of the second lunar month.

Wuhan is closed for thirty-two days.

The Gate of Heaven is sealed for thirty-one days.

In the afternoon, I will eat in a casserole dish of stew served in a bowl of cold, chopsticks are also handy on the bowl. Mother-in-law saw, said you this is for Dad Ready! Uncle also smiled to answer: afraid of what, Dad eat you can also eat. I can't help but wonder, perhaps this behavior of mine in the mother-in-law's eyes is an act of worship? Reading my grandmother in the evening as a ghost, I felt it was an interesting topic to talk about -- At least I could brush off today's diary.

Speaking of mother-in-law although a lifetime "blind" , but in our family seems to be a "fairy" . At home I, and a few of my cousins grandchildren, were living mother-in-law dream. I was a big but meatless cow, as if my cousin was a strapping bull -- although he and I were both six feet tall, he was certainly more strapping than I was. Years ago, he said he dreamed of a bull. He asked his uncle if his cousin had a baby. The answer was yes. In addition to dream have a hand, remember the childhood cold is not good, mother-in-law will also get up at midnight, with a bowl of water set chopsticks, while reading a word, while burning paper prayer. It is funny to say, dad is the most can not see mother-in-law believe these. Did Not expect to go first, was mother-in-law and home as a Bodhisattva bless. Mother-in-law sometimes body gratuitous pain, mouth will also say: Is Not Ghost old man and can not pass her...

I did not understand the mother-in-law's behavior, was "educated" arbitrary that this is a feudal superstition. Later, it was found that for the people who have no belief today, the only inheritance is probably the worship of ancestors. "As early as the Shang and Zhou Dynasties, the ancestors who became "ghosts and Gods" were believed to be able to bless or bring misfortune to future generations. Out of fear of their ancestors and seeking the benefits of the world, ancestor worship and ancestor worship were formed. "ancestor worship is arguably the most influential, longest-lasting, and most compulsory faith in China. "

"For the Chinese who do not believe in an absolute God, ancestor worship gives immortality to the mortal body. Ancestor worship means that people believe that their lives are handed down from distant ancestors and will be handed down into the future. In this way, the individual transcends the limits of time in the present and is placed in an eternal stream of time from the past to the future. Therefore, individual survival has significance: The individual body carries the family value, the lack of this link means the interruption of the family value inheritance. Therefore, the individual must treat his life well, which is required by his ancestors and their descendants."

"although the Chinese people have a strong emphasis on faith and utilitarian characteristics. If the Buddha does not work, you can choose to give up. But ancestor worship is not, regardless of whether the efficacy, can not be abandoned, this is the basic principle of life. Even if you believe in Buddhism, Taoism and other religions, you still must not worship your ancestors. This kind of ancestor worship is an important mechanism for the Chinese people to settle down and live. The life of the flesh is short, and the death of life is frightening. If death is the end, then life has no meaning. Individuals who do not feel the meaning of life will not be responsible for their own lives, nor for the lives of others, nor for society, and social order will collapse."

"Therefore, ancestor worship has an important social function, which is best summed up by Zengzi's words: "When one is careful to pursue the distant, the People's virtue is thicker. " Taking funeral seriously and offering sacrifices to ancestors sincerely mean that an individual knows that he is a link in the flow of time and a member of the community of temporality. Thus, the individual will restrain his behavior, which is the premise of virtue. If everyone in the society can self-discipline, it will naturally form a good social order."

When we think we are the spirit of all things, when we think we can be higher, faster and stronger, when we get used to controlling the killing and repressing... So nature has made "plague" and "Great Scrofula" to remind us that death and destruction are really close to us, and that our arrogance and ignorance is a joke. Therefore, always be in awe and refrain from doing anything.
